Package: WBreader
Type: Package
Title: Read and transform data from World Bank Database 
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jaroslaw Leski
Maintainer: The package maintainer <j.leski@student.uw.edu.pl>
Description: The package was created to easily load data downloaded from Worldbank.    It accepts both csv and xlsx. The PrettyValue parameter creates a new column with readable and easy to present values.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
